des:
Get unofficial to-the-minute stats & fun facts on the Texans by Fresh Digital Group. This skill isn’t sponsored or endorsed by the Texans.

Here’s some ways you can use the skill. We have given you many different ways for you to talk to Alexa:



General Updates:


Alexa, ask Texans Fan how are the Texans doing? 

Alexa, ask Texans Fan who do the Texans play next?

Alexa, ask Texans Fan J.J. Watt (or any player's First name, Last name) touchdown update. 



Fun Facts about the Texans:


Alexa, ask Texans Fan to tell me some trivia about the Texans. 

Alexa, ask Texans Fan how many Super Bowls have the Texans won?
